Vision:
    The basketball score tallying system records score to both competing teams in a basket ball league.
Mission:
    Create a simple tallying system
Objectives:
    * Within 2 hours the system will be usable
Principles:
    Simple user friendly system
Feature List:
    * Records the score given to a team
    * Can tally from points to points
Acceptance Criteria
    * Records the score given from a team
        - A score is recorded every time a player scores.
    * Can tally from points to points
        - The score will automatically tally every score input.